publicwhip.minor-heading: African Caribbean and Pacific Countries: EC External Trade

ques.p: To ask the Secretary of State for International Development when his Department's website will be updated in relation to the conclusion of economic partnership agreements by the 31 December 2007 deadline.

reply.p: The Department for International Development's website pages on Economic Partnership Agreements were updated on 10 December 2007 and again on 14 January 2008.
